text: "Jaded" is a 2023 song by Miley Cyrus and is the third single from her eighth studio album Endless Summer Vacation. It went to number 27 in the United Kingdom, number 56 in the United States, number 30 in Iceland and Canada, number 75 in Australia and number 21 in Ireland. ==References== Category:2023 songs Category:2020s ballads Category:Pop ballads Category:Rock ballads Category:Miley Cyrus songs Category:Pop rock songs
